name: Desktop page functionality
description: As a user I want to check desktop page and add product into cart

children.name: User should be able to add product to cart successfully
Given I am on Home page
When I mouse hover and click on currency dropdown
And I mouse hover and click on  £ Pound Sterling
And I mouse hover on "Desktops" Tab and click
And I call selectMenu method and pass the menu "Show AllDesktops"
And I select Sort By position to "Name (Z - A)"
And I select product "HTC Touch HD"
And I should see product text "HTC Touch HD"
And I select qty "1"
And I click on add to cart button
And I should see the message "Success: You have added HTC Touch HD to your shopping cart!"
And I click on shopping cart link into success message
Then I should see the "Shopping Cart" text
